data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT! FLORIDA WATERFRONT PARADISE AT ITS FINEST. Don’t miss this AMAZING COASTAL KEY WEST STYLE WATERFRONT HOME with the Gulf of Mexico in your Backyard. WATERFRONT VIEWS from Almost Every Room. Featuring 52 Feet of Seawall with some of the most stunning views in the Gulf Landings Community. From the moment You enter via the Double Entry Doors. All flooring is Upgraded and Updated on both floors, this Exceptionally Maintained Spacious, Bright, and Open Floorplan Features 5 Bedrooms, 4 Baths, Plus an Additional Bonus Living Space. This Bonus Living Space Area Has Many Possibilities to Include Recreational Room, Play Room, Office, Workout Room, Party Room, In-Law Suite to name but a Few. Additionally this Area Features ground floor access and direct access to the pool. The main living area is on the second floor. You Are Welcomed With an Abundance Of Natural Light as well a Luxury Vinyl Laminate Flooring Throughout. Enjoy the Spacious Living Area Overlooking the Backyard and Water-views This area includes the Spacious Kitchen with Stainless Steel appliance package and Granite Counters Tops and Plenty of Cabinetry. Eat in space in the kitchen, Breakfast Bar big enough for the whole family. Open floor plan includes the large formal dining area with Bay Window. The Master Suite has the most amazing water views to wake up to and is adjoined by a beautiful bathroom & Walk-In Closet. Granite Counters and Coastal Colors Make this Feel like a True Beach Home. This Level Also Features a Sizeable Laundry Room with Additional Storage Cabinets. For an Even Greater View Of the Water & Lots of Versatility to Arrange Your Furnishings in the upstairs Greatroom. Additional Guest Bathroom and 2 Guest Bedrooms that Lead out to One of the Balcony That Overlook the front, perfect place to sit & relax. The downstairs (first floor) includes a Family room, Formal living area with a wood burning fireplace. An additional Master ensuite, guest bedroom and an additional bathroom.  Direct access takes you to the beautiful pool area with two pergolas, sitting area with awning for shade, dog run, seawall and floating dock. . The pool deck is available For Year Round Enjoyment. The Pool Area With a Beautiful 6' deep Saltwater Pool is Truly an Enjoyable Space to Hangout or Entertain. This Area Features Custom Sitting Areas and Fire-Pit to Enjoy as a Further Feature to This Amazing Home. Enjoy the Wildlife, From Exotic Birds, Manatees, Local Dolphins Plus Enjoy The Amazing and Tranquil Sunsets. This is Truly an Oasis in The Air. Want to Hit the Water? You Have Several Options, launch your boat at the community boat ramp and mozy over to the Floating Dock or Launch Your Paddle Boards or Kayaks. Head Out to the Gulf of Mexico in Minutes Via the Chanel with Amazing Views Before Hitting the Open Seas.The Home Also Features a Side Fenced Yard For the Pets or for The Family to Enjoy - You Truly are Spoiled For Choice. The Roof was Replaced in 2017. Literally a Block away you can Enjoy the Use of the Gulf Landings Clubhouse, Pool, Tennis Courts & become a Member of the "Gulf Harbors Beach Club" which is a private Community Beach for just a nominal yearly fee $200 and is Exclusive to Those that Reside in the Area. Close to Schools, Beaches,Entertainment,Shopping,Multiple Golf Courses,Airports and Much Much More. All measurements to be verified by buyer. Survey and elevation Certificate available
